    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_5_4103-4159",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4103-4159",
      "markText": "社会，在以往，大都有个突飞猛进的时期。隔着一个时期，就停滞不进了。再阅若干时，又可以突飞猛进起来。已而复归于停滞",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4103&rangeEnd=4159",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4103&rangeEnd=4159"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_5_1933-2029",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1933-2029",
      "markText": "其实政治只是表面上的事情。政治的活动，全靠社会做根柢。社会，实在政治的背后，做了无数更广大、更根本的事情。不明白社会，是断不能明白政治的。所以现在讲历史的人，都不但着重于政治，而要着重于文化。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1933&rangeEnd=2029",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1933&rangeEnd=2029"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_12_779-842",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "779-842",
      "markText": "这实在是一个惊人的文化扩张。其原因何在呢？居于边地之国，因为和异族接近，以竞争磨砺而强，而其疆域亦易于拓展，该是其中最主要的。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=779&rangeEnd=842",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=779&rangeEnd=842"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_5_375-402",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "375-402",
      "markText": "历史，究竟是怎样一种学问？研究了它，究竟有什么用处呢？",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=375&rangeEnd=402",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=375&rangeEnd=402"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_5_1464-1526",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1464-1526",
      "markText": "史学之所求，不外乎：（一）搜求既往的事实，（二）加以解释，（三）用以说明现社会，（四）因以推测未来，而指示我们以进行的途径。",
      "totalCount": 99,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1464&rangeEnd=1526",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1464&rangeEnd=1526"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_5_2241-2312",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2241-2312",
      "markText": "（一）由其有特异的脑筋，能想出种种法子；（二）而其手和足全然分开，能制造种种工具，以遂行其计划；（三）又有语言以互相交通，而其扩大的即为文字。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2241&rangeEnd=2312",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2241&rangeEnd=2312"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_17_3203-3240",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "3203-3240",
      "markText": "汉武帝的用兵，是很不得法的，他不用功臣宿将，而专用卫青、霍去病等椒房之亲。",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=3203&rangeEnd=3240",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=3203&rangeEnd=3240"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_5_538-574",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "538-574",
      "markText": "世界上哪有真正相同的事情？所谓相同，都是察之不精，误以不同之事为同罢了。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=538&rangeEnd=574",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=538&rangeEnd=574"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_12_7257-7276",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "7257-7276",
      "markText": "有一个邀赏的机会。该是其最重要的原因。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=7257&rangeEnd=7276",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=7257&rangeEnd=7276"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_17_520-545",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "520-545",
      "markText": "文、景两帝亦只是个寻常人，凡事都只会蹈常习故之故。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=520&rangeEnd=545",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=520&rangeEnd=545"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_5_3168-3195",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3168-3195",
      "markText": "文化本是人类控制环境的行为，环境不同，文化自因之而异。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3168&rangeEnd=3195",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3168&rangeEnd=3195"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_8_2456-2484",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2456-2484",
      "markText": "所以追求民族的起源，实当求之于考古学，而不当求之于历史。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2456&rangeEnd=2484",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2456&rangeEnd=2484"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_5_3340-3377",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3340-3377",
      "markText": "所以文化优的，常思推行其文化于文化相异之群，以冀改良其生活，共谋人类的幸福",
      "totalCount": 78,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3340&rangeEnd=3377",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3340&rangeEnd=3377"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_5_951-965",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "951-965",
      "markText": "向来读书的人，就有些迂腐气。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=951&rangeEnd=965",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=951&rangeEnd=965"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_15_2756-2811",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "2756-2811",
      "markText": "秦始皇，向来都说他是暴君，把他的好处一笔抹杀了，其实这是冤枉的。看以上所述，他的政治实在是抱有一种伟大的理想的",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=2756&rangeEnd=2811",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=2756&rangeEnd=2811"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_25_5058-5107",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "5058-5107",
      "markText": "侯景遂反，进陷台城（南朝之宫城），梁武帝忧愤而崩。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300102198&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=5058&rangeEnd=5107",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8532170813ab8e6bg018a5a?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=5058&rangeEnd=5107"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300102198_45_3734-3758",
      "chapterUid": 45,
      "range": "3734-3758",
      "markText": "于是服务婚渐变为买卖婚，女子的地位，又形低落了。",
